Package: signal
Title: Signal processing
Version: 0.7-0
Date: 2011-05-12
Author: For Details on the authors of original functions (e.g. ported from Octave) 
  see the code and help files. Ported to R by Tom Short <tshort@eprisolutions.com>. 
  Later modifications by Uwe Ligges, Sarah Schnackenberg, Hans-Werner Borchers.
Maintainer: Uwe Ligges <ligges@statistik.tu-dortmund.de>
Depends: R (>= 2.10.0), stats, graphics, grDevices, MASS
Suggests: pracma
Description: A set of generally Matlab/Octave-compatible signal processing
  functions. Includes filter generation utilities, filtering functions,
  resampling routines, and visualization of filter models. It also
  includes interpolation functions and some Matlab comparability
  functions.
License: GPL-2
